# Power BI Training Resources

Explore these Microsoft resources to enhance your Power BI skills and knowledge.

## Microsoft Learn for Power BI

- **Power BI Learning Paths**
  - Explore comprehensive learning paths to build skills in modeling, visualizing, and analyzing data with Power BI.
  - [Visit Microsoft Learn for Power BI](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/powerplatform/power-bi)

## Microsoft Certified: Power BI Data Analyst Associate

- **Certification Program**
  - Demonstrate your expertise in Power BI by earning a Microsoft certification.
  - [Learn more about the certification](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/credentials/certifications/data-analyst-associate/)

## Power BI Video Series

- **Video Tutorials**
  - Access a series of video tutorials and demos to learn various aspects of Power BI.
  - [Explore Power BI videos](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/fundamentals/videos)

## Power BI Community

- **Forums and Discussions**
  - Join the Power BI community to connect with experts and peers, ask questions, and share knowledge.
  - [Visit the Power BI Community](https://community.fabric.microsoft.com/t5/Power-BI-forums/ct-p/powerbi)

## Power BI Support

- **Self-Service Guidance**
  - Access support resources and self-service guidance for common Power BI issues.
  - [Learn more about Power BI support](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/support/)

## Power BI Blog

- **Latest News and Updates**
  - Stay informed about the latest features, updates, and best practices for Power BI.
  - [Read the Power BI Blog](https://powerbi.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/)

## Power BI Documentation

- **In-Depth Articles**
  - Access detailed articles covering Power BI tools, features, and advanced techniques.
  - [Explore Power BI documentation](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/)

## Microsoft Power BI Courses on Coursera

- **Online Courses**
  - Enroll in online courses to learn Power BI skills from industry experts.
  - [Explore Power BI courses on Coursera](https://www.coursera.org/courses?query=microsoft+power+bi)

## Power BI Dashboard in a Day

- **Hands-On Workshops**
  - Participate in free, hands-on workshops to learn how to build Power BI dashboards.
  - [Sign up for a workshop](https://powerbi.microsoft.com/en-us/diad/)

## Microsoft Power BI Data Analyst Course

- **Course PL-300T00-A**
  - Learn best practices for modeling, visualizing, and analyzing data with Power BI.
  - [Learn more about the course](https://learn.microsoft.com/nb-no/training/courses/pl-300t00)

By leveraging these resources, you can deepen your understanding of Power BI and enhance your data analysis capabilities.
